apos>May<apos><closebracket>=<apos>mai<apos><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>mois<openbracket><apos>June<apos><closebracket>=<apos>juin<apos><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>mois<openbracket><apos>July<apos><closebracket>=<apos>juillet<apos><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>mois<openbracket><apos>August<apos><closebracket>=<apos>ao<u00fb>t<apos><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>mois<openbracket><apos>September<apos><closebracket>=<apos>septembre<apos><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>mois<openbracket><apos>October<apos><closebracket>=<apos>octobre<apos><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>mois<openbracket><apos>November<apos><closebracket>=<apos>novembre<apos><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>mois<openbracket><apos>December<apos><closebracket>=<apos>d<u00e9>cembre<apos><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>fr=False<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>for<space>keys<space>in<space>mois:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>if<space>keys<space>in<space>feature.getAttribute<openparen><apos>_citationDate_fr<apos><closeparen>:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>feature.setAttribute<openparen><apos>_citationDate_fr<apos><comma>feature.getAttribute<openparen><apos>_citationDate_fr<apos><closeparen>.replace<openparen>keys<comma>mois<openbracket>keys<closebracket><closeparen><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>fr=True<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>if<space>not<space>fr:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>feature.setAttribute<openparen><apos>_error_date<apos><comma><apos>Impossible<space>de<space>mapper<space>la<space>date<space>%s<space>en<space>fran<u00e7>ais<apos>%<openparen>feature.getAttribute<openparen><apos>_citationDate_fr<apos><closeparen><closeparen><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.pyoutput<openparen>feature<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space>def<space>close<openparen>self<closeparen>:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>pass    OUTPUT PYOUTPUT FEATURE_TYPE PythonCaller_5_OUTPUT
